<h2 id="why">Why support?</h2>

<p>
  convertFlow is a one-person project. It runs entirely in your browser — no servers,
  no accounts, no telemetry by default. That also means there's no upsell path,
  no premium tier, no enterprise SaaS waiting in the wings to subsidize it.
</p>

<p>
  Hosting is cheap (Cloudflare Pages) and the code is open. The expensive part is
  the time it takes to keep the format presets, embedding prices, and provider
  schemas current. Every dollar makes it easier to spend more of that time on the
  tool and less on a day job.
</p>

<h2 id="buy-coffee">Buy a coffee</h2>

<p>
  Smallest, easiest way. One-off contribution, no recurring charge, no account
  needed beyond a card.
</p>

<div class="cta-row">
  <a class="cta-primary" href="https://buymeacoffee.com/convertflow" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
    ☕ Buy me a coffee →
  </a>
  <span class="cta-aside">$5 / $10 / custom</span>
</div>

<p>
  If you used convertFlow to ship a fine-tune or build a RAG pipeline that's earning you
  or your team money, this is the easiest "thanks" button on the internet.
</p>

<h2 id="sponsor">Sponsor a feature</h2>

<p>
  Need something specific? File-format support, a particular preset, a custom
  validator, a private deployment? Sponsor a feature and it ships within 1–2 weeks
  with your name in the release notes.
</p>

<p>
  Email <a href="mailto:hello@convertflow.live">hello@convertflow.live</a> with what you need.
  Typical sponsor rates: $200 small feature · $500 medium · $1,000+ provider integration / major UI.
</p>

<h2 id="ads">Advertise here</h2>

<p>
  The small sponsor slot at the bottom of the app is available for relevant
  developer-tool / LLM-tooling / data-engineering products.
</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Audience:</strong> developers preparing fine-tuning datasets and RAG pipelines (mostly North America + EU, mid-to-senior engineers).</li>
  <li><strong>Placement:</strong> non-intrusive footer slot, visible across all tabs, dismissible by the user.</li>
  <li><strong>Rate:</strong> $300 / month for the single slot (one sponsor at a time, no auctions, no tracking pixels).</li>
</ul>

<p>
  Get in touch: <a href="mailto:hello@convertflow.live?subject=Sponsorship">hello@convertflow.live</a>
</p>

<h2 id="free-options">Free ways to help</h2>

<ul>
  <li>★ <strong>Star <a href="https://github.com/abhijathk/convertFlow" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">the GitHub repo</a></strong> — visibility is the cheapest thing you can give.</li>
  <li>📝 <strong>Write about it</strong> — a blog post / tweet / r/LocalLLaMA mention all help discovery.</li>
  <li>🐛 <strong>Report a bug</strong> — <a href="mailto:hello@convertflow.live?subject=Bug report">email a bug report</a> (or open a GitHub issue) with a sample dataset and we'll fix it fast.</li>
  <li>💡 <strong>Suggest a preset or format</strong> — if your provider/model isn't in the list, tell us and we'll add it.</li>
  <li>🔗 <strong>Link to it</strong> — from your team wiki, docs, or tutorial. Backlinks help search rank.</li>
</ul>

<p>
  Thanks for reading. Hope convertFlow keeps being useful.
</p>

